# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:22
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Instalacija"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:24
msgid ""
"The latest official **stable** version of OpenShot Video Editor for Linux, "
"Mac, Chrome OS, and Windows can be downloaded from the official download "
"page at https://www.openshot.org/download/. You can find our latest "
"**unstable** versions (i.e. daily builds) at https://www.openshot.org/"
"download#daily (these versions are updated very frequently, and often "
"contain many improvements not yet released in our stable build)."
msgstr ""
"Najnoviju službenu **stabilnu** verziju OpenShot Video Editora za Linux, "
"Mac, Chrome OS i Windows možete preuzeti sa službene stranice za preuzimanje "
"na https://www.openshot.org/download/. Najnovije **nestabilne** verzije (tj. "
"dnevne verzije) možete pronaći na https://www.openshot.org/download#daily "
"(ove verzije se vrlo često ažuriraju i često sadrže mnoge poboljšanja koja "
"još nisu objavljena u našoj stabilnoj verziji)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:32
msgid "Clean Install"
msgstr "Čista instalacija"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you are upgrading from a previous version of OpenShot or are experiencing "
"a crash or error message after launching OpenShot, please see :ref:"
"`preferences_reset_ref` for instructions on clearing the previous ``openshot."
"settings`` file (for a clean install with **default preferences**)."
msgstr ""
"Ako nadograđujete s prethodne verzije OpenShota ili imate pad programa ili "
"poruku o pogrešci nakon pokretanja OpenShota, molimo pogledajte :ref:"
"`preferences_reset_ref` za upute o brisanju prethodne datoteke ``openshot."
"settings`` (za čistu instalaciju s **zadanim postavkama**)."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:39
msgid "Windows (Installer)"
msgstr "Windows (Instaler)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:41
msgid ""
"Download the Windows installer from the `official download page <https://www."
"openshot.org/download/>`_ (the download page contains both 64-bit and 32-bit "
"versions), double click it, and follow the directions on screen. Once "
"completed, OpenShot will be installed and available in your Start menu."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite Windows instalacijski program sa `službene stranice za preuzimanje "
"<https://www.openshot.org/download/>`_ (stranica za preuzimanje sadrži "
"verzije za 64-bit i 32-bit), dvaput kliknite na njega i slijedite upute na "
"ekranu. Nakon dovršetka, OpenShot će biti instaliran i dostupan u vašem "
"izborniku Start."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:50
msgid "Windows (Portable)"
msgstr "Windows (Prijenosna verzija)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:52
msgid ""
"If you need to install OpenShot on Windows without Administrator "
"permissions, we also support a portable installation process. Download the "
"Windows installer from the `official download page <https://www.openshot.org/"
"download/>`_, open the command prompt, and type the following commands:"
msgstr ""
"Ako trebate instalirati OpenShot na Windows bez administratorskih prava, "
"također podržavamo prijenosni način instalacije. Preuzmite Windows "
"instalacijski program sa `službene stranice za preuzimanje <https://www."
"openshot.org/download/>`_, otvorite naredbeni redak i upišite sljedeće "
"naredbe:"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:67 ../installation.rst:181
msgid "Mac"
msgstr "Mac"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:69
msgid ""
"Download the DMG file from the `official download page <https://www.openshot."
"org/download/>`_, double click it, and then drag the OpenShot application "
"icon into your **Applications** shortcut. This is very similar to how most "
"Mac applications are installed. Now launch OpenShot from `Launchpad` or "
"`Applications` in Finder."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite DMG datoteku sa `službene stranice za preuzimanje <https://www."
"openshot.org/download/>`_, dvaput kliknite na nju, a zatim povucite ikonu "
"aplikacije OpenShot u prečac **Applications**. Ovo je vrlo slično načinu na "
"koji se instalira većina Mac aplikacija. Sada pokrenite OpenShot iz "
"`Launchpad` ili `Applications` u Finderu."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:77
msgid "Linux (AppImage)"
msgstr "Linux (AppImage)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:79
msgid ""
"Most Linux distributions have a version of OpenShot in their software "
"repositories, which can be installed using your package manager / software "
"store. However, these packaged versions are often very outdated (be sure to "
"check the version number: :guilabel:`Help→About OpenShot`). For this reason, "
"we recommend installing an AppImage from the `official download page "
"<https://www.openshot.org/download/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Većina Linux distribucija ima verziju OpenShota u svojim softverskim "
"spremištima, koju možete instalirati pomoću upravitelja paketa ili trgovine "
"softverom. Međutim, ove pakirane verzije često su vrlo zastarjele "
"(provjerite broj verzije: :guilabel:`Pomoć→O OpenShotu`). Iz tog razloga "
"preporučujemo instalaciju AppImage verzije sa `službene stranice za "
"preuzimanje <https://www.openshot.org/download/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:85
msgid ""
"Once downloaded, right click on the AppImage, choose Properties, and mark "
"the file as **Executable**. Finally, double click the AppImage to launch "
"OpenShot. If double clicking does not launch OpenShot, you can also right "
"click on the AppImage, and choose `Execute` or `Run`. For a detailed guide "
"on installing our AppImage and creating a launcher for it, see our `AppImage "
"Installation Guide <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/AppImage-"
"Installation>`_."
msgstr ""
"Nakon preuzimanja, kliknite desnom tipkom miša na AppImage, odaberite "
"Svojstva i označite datoteku kao **Izvršnu**. Na kraju, dvaput kliknite na "
"AppImage da pokrenete OpenShot. Ako dvostruki klik ne pokrene OpenShot, "
"možete također kliknuti desnom tipkom na AppImage i odabrati `Izvrši` ili "
"`Pokreni`. Za detaljan vodič o instalaciji našeg AppImage i stvaranju "
"pokretača, pogledajte naš `Vodič za instalaciju AppImage <https://github.com/"
"OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/AppImage-Installation>`_."

