msgid "Install AppImage Launcher"
msgstr "Instalirajte AppImage Launcher"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:105
msgid ""
"If you plan on using OpenShot often, you will probably want an integrated "
"launcher for our AppImage. We recommend using AppImageLauncher, which is the "
"officially supported way to launch (and manage) AppImage files on your Linux "
"desktop. If you are on a Debian-based distro (Ubuntu, Mint, etc...), there "
"is an official AppImageLauncher PPA:"
msgstr ""
"Ako planirate često koristiti OpenShot, vjerojatno ćete htjeti integrirani "
"pokretač za naš AppImage. Preporučujemo korištenje AppImageLauncher-a, koji "
"je službeno podržani način za pokretanje (i upravljanje) AppImage datotekama "
"na vašem Linux desktopu. Ako koristite distribuciju temeljenu na Debianu "
"(Ubuntu, Mint itd.), postoji službeni AppImageLauncher PPA:"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:117
msgid "Linux (PPA)"
msgstr "Linux (PPA)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:119
msgid ""
"For Debian-based Linux distributions (Ubuntu, Mint, etc...), we also have a "
"PPA (Personal Package Archive), which adds our official OpenShot software "
"repository to your package manager, making it possible to install our latest "
"version, without relying on our AppImages."
msgstr ""
"Za Linux distribucije temeljene na Debianu (Ubuntu, Mint itd.) također imamo "
"PPA (Personal Package Archive), koja dodaje naše službeno OpenShot "
"softversko spremište vašem upravitelju paketa, omogućujući instalaciju "
"najnovije verzije bez oslanjanja na naše AppImage datoteke."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:124
msgid "Stable PPA (Contains only official releases)"
msgstr "Stabilni PPA (Sadrži samo službena izdanja)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:133
msgid "Daily PPA (Highly experimental and unstable, for testers)"
msgstr "Dnevni PPA (Vrlo eksperimentalno i nestabilno, za testere)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:142
msgid "Chrome OS (Chromebook)"
msgstr "Chrome OS (Chromebook)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:144
msgid ""
"Chrome OS supports Linux apps, but this feature is off by default. You can "
"turn it on in *Settings*. Once Linux is enabled, you can install and run "
"OpenShot Linux AppImages on any *x86-based* Chromebook. The command below "
"will download our AppImage and configure your system to run OpenShot "
"successfully."
msgstr ""
"Chrome OS podržava Linux aplikacije, ali je ova značajka isključena prema "
"zadanim postavkama. Možete je uključiti u *Postavkama*. Nakon što je Linux "
"omogućen, možete instalirati i pokretati OpenShot Linux AppImage na bilo "
"kojem Chromebooku temeljenom na *x86*. Sljedeća naredba će preuzeti naš "
"AppImage i konfigurirati vaš sustav za uspješan rad OpenShota."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:149
msgid "Navigate to *chrome://os-settings/crostini* (Copy/Paste)"
msgstr "Idite na *chrome://os-settings/crostini* (kopirajte/zalijepite)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:150
msgid "Under \"Linux (Beta)\" select \"Turn On\". Default values are fine."
msgstr ""
"Pod \"Linux (Beta)\" odaberite \"Uključi\". Zadane vrijednosti su u redu."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:152
msgid ""
"When the Terminal appears (i.e. black window), Copy/Paste the following "
"command:"
msgstr ""
"Kad se pojavi Terminal (crni prozor), kopirajte i zalijepite sljedeću "
"naredbu:"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:152
msgid ""
"``bash <(wget -O - http://openshot.org/files/chromeos/install-stable.sh)``"
msgstr ""
"``bash <(wget -O - http://openshot.org/files/chromeos/install-stable.sh)``"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:155
msgid "Previous Versions"
msgstr "Prethodne verzije"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:157
msgid ""
"To download old versions of OpenShot Video Editor, you can visit https://"
"github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tags. Click on the version number you need, "
"and scroll to the bottom, under the release notes. You will find download "
"links for each operating system. Download the appropriate version for your "
"computer, and follow the installation instructions above."
msgstr ""
"Za preuzimanje starih verzija OpenShot Video Editora, možete posjetiti "
"https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tags. Kliknite na broj verzije koja "
"vam treba i pomaknite se do dna, ispod bilješki o izdanju. Tamo ćete pronaći "
"poveznice za preuzimanje za svaki operativni sustav. Preuzmite odgovarajuću "
"verziju za vaše računalo i slijedite gore navedene upute za instalaciju."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:162
msgid ""
"NOTE: Projects (\\*.osp) made with newer versions of OpenShot Video Editor "
"might not support older versions."
msgstr ""
"NAPOMENA: Projekti (\\*.osp) izrađeni novijim verzijama OpenShot Video "
"Editora možda neće biti podržani u starijim verzijama."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:165
msgid "Uninstall"
msgstr "Deinstaliraj"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:167
msgid ""
"To fully uninstall OpenShot from your system, you must **manually delete** "
"the ``.openshot_qt`` folder: ``~/.openshot_qt/`` or ``C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\."
"openshot_qt\\``, which contains all settings and files used by OpenShot. Be "
"sure to **backup** any recovery files of your existing projects first (\\*."
"osp files). Please see :ref:`preferences_reset_ref` for instructions on "
"clearing the previous ``openshot.settings`` file (for a clean install with "
"**default preferences**)."
msgstr ""
"Da biste u potpunosti deinstalirali OpenShot s vašeg sustava, morate **ručno "
"izbrisati** mapu ``.openshot_qt``: ``~/.openshot_qt/`` ili ``C:"
"\\Users\\USERNAME\\.openshot_qt\\``, koja sadrži sve postavke i datoteke "
"koje koristi OpenShot. Prije toga obavezno napravite **sigurnosnu kopiju** "
"svih datoteka za oporavak postojećih projekata (\\*.osp datoteke). Molimo "
"pogledajte :ref:`preferences_reset_ref` za upute o brisanju prethodne "
"datoteke ``openshot.settings`` (za čistu instalaciju s **zadanim "
"postavkama**)."

